{"tid":784762,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"窮撚無資格怕鬼","createTime":"2018-08-18T15:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T16:24:55.000Z","uid":117332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3bffcdf0c464dfbf30c888a2c550d791b386bf00","tid":784762,"uid":117332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T15:49:21.000Z","msg":"窮人無資格怕鬼<br />\n<br />\n高危職業保安或者流浪漢可以無啦啦被野捉走慘死馬桶。或者低薪新人護士都係死先。<br />\n<br />\n電影橋段一家人去左一間新屋，而間屋有啲靈異野，一家人歷盡危險，結局搬屋就可以化解危機，窮撚如果搬得入一間屋，都無得話搬就搬。<br />\n<br />\n一班人去左泰國旅行惹左野，起碼有錢可以求助高人。<br />\n<br />\n或者一班人為錢定以為有個荀工做點知中伏，有錢人根本唔使以身犯險。<br />\n<br />\n而普通鬼節禁忌窮人無得避，窮撚番夜班無得避搭夜班車，制服黑色無得避著黑衫。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n細膽窮撚表示好驚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  希望撞鬼啲鬼都會避窮鬼"},{"pid":"48fe91d2df6aea436cb5da54216c60138a5a2d99","tid":784762,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T15:58:14.000Z","msg":"護士起薪三皮野 邊撚度低薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b8151c3454e896dc5fefe9caca777357df2d52","tid":784762,"uid":117332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48fe91d2df6aea436cb5da54216c60138a5a2d99","tid":784762,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T15:58:14.000Z","msg":"護士起薪三皮野 邊撚度低薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T16:24:55.000Z","msg":"你岩"}]}